'''Johann Sebastian Bach''' kɛ [[Caama (Allemagne)|caama]] tʋ. Ɛlakɩ soo tʋmɩyɛ yaa ɛkɛ soo maɖʋ nɛ wendu lɩzɩyʋ sɔsɔ nɔɔyʋ kɛ caama ɛjaɖɛ nɖɩ ɖɩ-taa. Ɛkɛ ɖɔɖɔ wendu teu n̄ɔɔzɩyʋ soo mabʋ taa.

[[File:Brandenburg No4-1 BWV1049.ogg|thumb|Brandenburg No4-1 BWV1049]]

Ɖɩ-taa peeɖe palʋla-ɩ [[lakɩŋ fenaɣ]] taa kɛ kɩyakʋ hiŋ naadozo nɛ kʋɖʋmʋʋ yaa n̄ɩŋgʋ wiye (31), yaa pʋtɔtɔ lakɩŋ fenaɣ ŋga ka-taa, ɛlɛ efemiye nɛɛlɛ nɛ kʋɖʋmʋʋ (21) ) n̄ɩŋgʋ wiye kɛ pɩnaɣ 1685 n̄ɩŋga alɩwaatʋ taa.

[[File:Denkmal Johann Sebastian Bach Leipzig 2011.jpg|thumb|Denkmal Johann Sebastian Bach Leipzig 2011]]

E-egeetiye kɩlʋlʋyɛ payaɣ size Eisenach. Ɛsɩba [[hasɩyaɖɛ fenaɣ]] taa kɛ efemiye nɛɛlɛ nɛ nutozo (28) n̄ɩŋgʋ wiye kɛ pɩnaɣ 1750 n̄ɩŋga taa. Bach tɛ samaɣ hɔʋʋ taa lɛ, Johann Sebastian Bach kɛ ɛyʋ yaa pɩɣa mɛɛsɛjɛba yaa mɛɛsɛgula. Ɛ-hɩɖɛ sɛwa ɖɩ-tɛ ɖɩkʋyɩ siŋŋ pɩkɩlɩ hɔʋʋ taa pɩɣa lɛɣsɩ.

[[File:Jsbach_bwv996_03.ogg|thumb|Lute suite in E minor]]

Ɖɩ-taɣsɔ ɖɔɖɔ size, ɛ-hɔʋʋ kɛna hɔʋʋ ŋgʋ kɩ-taa, caanaʋ tɛ soo nɛ minziiki tʋma laɖa kɩla wɛʋ yɔ. Caama ɛjaɖɛ hɛkʋ nɛ hɛkʋ taa ɛ-caɣ nɛ ɛla e-mʋsɩ tʋma kpeekpe nɛ ɛ-kɔɔ ɛtɛ.

Tovonum taa lɛ, ɛ-n̄ʋʋ taa ɖɔŋga yaa ɛka wɛ lɔŋ siŋŋ, ɛlɛ ɛtaapɩzɩ ehɩu tʋmɩyɛ naɖɩyɛ siŋŋ kɛ ɛ-n̄ʋʋ maɣzɩm ɖeɖe. Caama ɛjaɖɛ kɩlɩmwaa nabayɩ sakɩyɛ kaatɩla e-ɖoŋ kamaɣ ɖeu, nɛ paɖʋyɩ nesi. Pa-taa nɔɔyʋ hɩɖɛ yɔ : Frédéric le Grand kɛ Cantor de Leipzig hɔɔlʋʋ taa yaa ɖeɖe.

[[File:Quodlibet.jpg|thumb|Quodlibet]]

Ɖajaa Johann Sebastian Bach pɩsa soiɣa lɔŋ. Ɛ-caa nɛ ɛ-ɖalʋ sɔsɔ pɛhɛyɩna ɛtɛ tʋma kpeekpe kpɛlɩkɩtʋ liidiye. Ɛ-caa payaɣ size Johann Ambrosius Bach, nɛ ɛ-ɖalʋ sɔsɔ ɛlɛ lɛ Johann Christoph Bach. Ɛcɛyaa ɛ-tɩ ɛzɩma yɔ ɖʋna wɛ hʋnʋŋ nɛ pɛwɛ paɖʋyɩ nesi paa ɛzɩm taa.

Ɖajaa Bach lakɩ minziikinaa mba yɔ, mba yɔ [[Fiyoolɔɣ (violon)|fiyoolɔɣ]] nɛ [[alto]], nɛ pɩkɩlɩna klavɛsɛɛ, nɛ pɩtɛzɩna [[Orɩgɩ (Orgue)|Orɩgɩ]].

